487fbca0a1d65bc14011eedea6c4","tid":1644923,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"古伊卡林推動晒成個發展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"本書係咪寫點用妖精整核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下收唔收得番曬d伏線<br />\n幾個勢力家下要清一個<br />\n黑書後裔+男主team+雷頓恩應該目的都係類似<br />\n唔想妖精再投入戰場<br />\n但另一邊統一國+舊戰爭國聯合軍似乎想再打仗<br />\n所以想要力量<br />\n計埋妖精武器都唔知想點"},{"pid":"83d7e482627fd4d2a0633e42a2215fe563c78c8f","tid":1644923,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"仲以為頂到耐d,都係劇情殺<br />\n換轉恐怖片咁多一齊攻邊頂到<br />\n女主隻野,又或者講妖精到家下都唔明做緊乜<br />\n比人打傷會反映係個人身上<br />\n最新玩法係copy<br />\n一提完就到通街都係既?<br />\n仲以為第1集隻野只係傳說,同埋妖精會忽然間上身互打<br />\n原來係特別例子<br />\n但個教團又同女主條村有咩分別,都係當隻野神咁拜<br />\n主線都係去番上季最尾咁,變左係妖精武器使用者之間既戰鬥<br />\n睇下佢仲有咩大道理講"},{"pid":"b6dc72bcf0afdf04dd738b5c173960bdf8fca20c","tid":1644923,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"今集都收左幾多伏線下???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收齊本書係用黎整神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nconfirm左首相+多蘿西婭+後裔+雷係同一目的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妖精省就.......其實都預左<br />\n弗里個fd到底係幫邊面......真係睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea9611e34912599f55366762a43d9abc1b3b285","tid":1644923,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6dc72bcf0afdf04dd738b5c173960bdf8fca20c","tid":1644923,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"今集都收左幾多伏線下???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收齊本書係用黎整神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail